@baseUrl = http://localhost:3002
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: {{contentType}}

### --- AUTH ---

### Login User
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### Get Auth Token (Variables for subsequent requests)
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### Get My Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### --- PRODUCTS ---

### Get All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Create New Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Sony PlayStation 5",
  "price": 7500000,
  "stock": 10
}

### Update Product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Sony PlayStation 5 Slim",
  "price": 7200000,
  "stock": 15
}

### Delete Product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: {{contentType}}
